    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><strong>1.  Add GEM to environment file</strong>
```</p>

<h1>in config/environment.rb</h1>

<p>config.gem &lsquo;hoptoad_notifier&rsquo;
```</p>

<p><strong>2. Install gems</strong>
```</p>

<h1>from your Rails root:</h1>

<p>rake gems:install
rake gems:unpack GEM=hoptoad_notifier
```</p>

<p><strong>3. Generate hoptoad install using key</strong>
<code>
ruby script/generate hoptoad --api-key your_key_here
</code></p>
